data.actual_result: The closing quote shows as part of the link, and therefore makes it invalid.
data.expected_result: The quotes shouldn't show, the link should open normally.
data.short_description: Quotes to prevent a link from embedding break highlighting when the link ends by a closing parenthesis
data.steps_to_repro: - Post a link that ends with a closing parenthesis between "<>" - View it / click it from your Android device
